<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_13&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image displays a monochrome graphic icon, primarily composed of shades of black and white or gray. The central element is a bold, black plus sign, oriented vertically and horizontally, forming a cross shape. This black plus sign is perfectly centered within a smaller, distinct white square. This white square, with the black plus sign inside it, is then set against a larger, solid black square background. The overall appearance is clean, geometric, and indicative of an 'add' or 'expand' function, commonly seen in user interfaces."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_13.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PLUS SIGN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A black plus sign, centrally located within a white square. It consists of two intersecting bars of equal length and width."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_13.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SQUARE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A white square with a black border, serving as the background and container for the black plus sign. The area outside the square is black."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_13.jpg</data>
</node>
